    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实的管理体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的每个细节都尽可能真实地还原了电子竞技的世界。从与选手谈判合同到在比赛中做出复杂的战术决策，涵盖方方面面。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >团队管理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >接管现有的团队之一，或者从零开始创建自己的团队。选择团队的标志、球衣和颜色组合，打造一支通过赢得Major赛事而成为传奇的团队。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/942dc8071631b43dbd625254196837eb.poster.avif?t=1763041169\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/942dc8071631b43dbd625254196837eb.webm?t=1763041169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/942dc8071631b43dbd625254196837eb.mp4?t=1763041169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >真实的赛事和赛制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏采用了真实的赛事格式和规则，让您感受赢得世界上最具声望的赛事的荣耀。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >战术、训练与士气</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不同的地图需要不同的策略，您的任务是为每场比赛找到最佳策略。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >实时比赛模拟</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用暂停时间，调整战术并做出关键决策，扭转比赛局势，为自己赢得胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/3b98d89d355d35bd40e767c758342855.poster.avif?t=1763041169\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/3b98d89d355d35bd40e767c758342855.webm?t=1763041169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/3b98d89d355d35bd40e767c758342855.mp4?t=1763041169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >与选手和团队成员谈判</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过与选手和团队之间的详细合同谈判，您有多种选择来签下梦寐以求的选手。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >设施建设</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级团队设施的各个部分。设施等级越高，您获得的奖励也越大。然而，这一切都需要时间和金钱，因此请谨慎规划您的行动。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >财务管理</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >关注团队的财务状况。谈判有利可图的赞助合同，使您能够投资于更好的选手、更优质的训练和更完善的设施。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/be7fa2372ec5003d3b54989b23bcacb3.poster.avif?t=1763041169\" width=616 height=272 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/be7fa2372ec5003d3b54989b23bcacb3.webm?t=1763041169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3138060/extras/be7fa2372ec5003d3b54989b23bcacb3.mp4?t=1763041169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >突发状况</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为可能影响您的团队和计划的突发情况做好准备。选手的伤病、团队的意外变动或额外的财务支出可能会让您通往巅峰的道路变得更加艰难。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成为您梦想中的团队经理，并在<i>Esport Manager: Road to Major</i>中带领团队走向辉煌。您的成功取决于您的决策——您准备好接受挑战，成为下一位Major冠军吗？</p>",
